Name: Cowboy : Attack of Wild Animal
About the game: Cowboy : Attack of Wild animals is to avoid wild animals attacking the owner. You can avoid a dangerous moment by rushing or get over a crisis by hunting animals with a gun. Do not stop and keep moving! Then you will survive in the wild. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Main Features ■ Single Mode ■ Competition Mode(single) ■ Mulit Mode ■ Hide and Seek Mode ■ Various Obstacle ■ Upgrade -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
